casebody.data:
Wednesday, November 4,1998

MERIT DOCKET

98-1700. State v. Trent.

Allen App. No. 1-98-3. On review of order certifying a conflict. The court determines that no conflict exists within the meaning of S.Ct.Prac.R. IV(2)(B). See State v. Rush (1998), 83 Ohio St.3d 53, 697 N.E.2d 634. This cause is therefore dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
